flowchart LR
    subgraph Simulation["Simulation clinique"]
        Cases["Catalogue de cas\nchirurgie + complication + J postop"]
        Simulator["Simulateur Python\nbaseline J0 + trajectoire"]
        Cases --> Simulator
    end

    Simulator -->|MQTT QoS 1\npatients/{id}/vitals| Mosquitto["Mosquitto"]

    subgraph Backend["Backend FastAPI"]
        Consumer["Consumer MQTT\nvalidation + enrichissement"]
        Alerting["Alert engine\nalertes simples, combinees,\nhistoriques et actives"]
        Scoring["Scoring\ncriticite immediate + risque evolutif + ML"]
        LLM["IA clinique\nresume, pack clinique,\nscenario-review, priorisation"]
        Questionnaire["Questionnaire differentiel\ntronc commun + modules cibles"]
        Context["Contexte patient\nterrain + peri-op + complications discutees"]
        Consumer --> Alerting
        Consumer --> Scoring
        Questionnaire --> LLM
        Context --> LLM
    end

    Mosquitto --> Consumer

    Consumer -->|historique J0 -> maintenant\n+ live| Influx[("InfluxDB\nvitals + tendances")]
    Consumer -->|patients, alertes,\nnotes, feedback| Postgres[("PostgreSQL")]

    Influx --> Scoring
    Influx --> LLM
    Postgres --> Alerting
    Postgres --> LLM
    Alerting --> Postgres

    subgraph Frontend["Frontend React"]
        Patients["Page Patients\nmonitoring global + priorisation"]
        Detail["Page PatientDetail\ngraphes, alertes,\ncontexte, questionnaire, IA"]
        Export["Export CSV / PDF"]
    end

    Backend -->|REST| Patients
    Backend -->|REST| Detail
    Backend -->|WebSocket live| Patients
    Backend -->|WebSocket live| Detail
    Detail --> Export

    LLM -->|Ollama local\nMeditron ou fallback local| Ollama["Ollama"]
